BBCalc - Body Building Calculators
==================================

Description:

	BBCalc (Body Building Calculators) is a set of calculators related to
	bodybuilding and fitness topics.

Dependencies:

	* Python 2.3 or above
	* PyGTK 2.4 or above
	
	Application was tested to work on Ubuntu 7.10.
	
	Note: Please, write me a note if it's working in other environment and
	with the other dependencies than above.

Installation:

	TODO: Write installation instruction
	
	Just unzip and than run command 'make install' inside bbcalc directory.
	
